#GraphSort(layout='column',
	md-theme='graphsort',
	layout-gt-md='row',
	flex)
	//- Main content
	div(flex-gt-md='33')
		md-card(flex-gt-md='66',
			ng-if='welcomeMsgOpen',
			md-colors="::{backgroundColor: 'accent-700'}")
			md-card-title
				md-card-title-text
					span.md-headline Welcome to Graph Sort
			md-card-content
				p
					| Graph theory based entity resolution. Uses community detection sort strings.
			md-card-actions(layout="row" layout-align="end center")
				md-button.md-icon-button(ng-click='closeWelcomeMsg()')
					md-icon(md-font-library='material-icons')
						| close
		md-card
			md-card-title
				md-card-title-text
					span.md-headline Items to Sort
			md-card-content
				form(layout='column', flex)
					md-input-container
						label Enter items in a comma delimited format with quotations...
						textarea(rows='5')
			md-card-actions(layout='row', layout-align='end')
				md-button.md-primary.md-hue-5
					| Example 1
				md-button.md-primary.md-hue-5
					| Example 2
				md-button.md-primary.md-hue-5
					| Example 3
				md-button(md-colors="::{backgroundColor: 'accent-700'}")
					| Sort
	div(flex-gt-md='66', layout='row', flex)
		md-card(flex)
			//-md-progress-linear
			md-card-title
					md-card-title-text
						span.md-headline Results
			md-card-content#GraphOutput(layout='row')